画像ファイルにMatrix演算を実施(低速版)¶

In [1]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.image as mpimg
%matplotlib inline

# matrix 
mono_conv_matrix = [[0.3, 0.65, 0.5],
                    [0.3, 0.65, 0.5],
                    [0.3, 0.65, 0.5]]

def ty_matrix(img, mat):
    # R, G, B 
    r, g, b = np.dsplit(img, 3)
    
    # 
    ret_r = r * mat[0][0] + g * mat[0][1] + b * mat[0][2]
    ret_g = r * mat[1][0] + g * mat[1][1] + b * mat[1][2]
    ret_b = r * mat[2][0] + g * mat[2][1] + b * mat[2][2]
    
    # RGB
    ret_img = np.dstack( (ret_r, ret_g, ret_b) )

    return np.uint8(ret_img)
  
img = mpimg.imread('sample.jpg')

# matrix
out_img = ty_matrix(img, mono_conv_matrix)

# 
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,1) #  index 
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,2)
ax1.imshow(img)
ax2.imshow(out_img)

<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x1d2c2a23fd0>

適当なグラフを書く¶

$y = x^2$

In [34]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

sample_num = 1024
x = np.arange(sample_num) / (sample_num - 1) # [0:1]

#  x
print("== x value ==")
print(x)
print("== x value end == ")

y = x ** 2 

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(7,7)) # 
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,1,1)    #  index 
ax1.plot(x, y, linestyle='-', linewidth=3, label='x^2')
plt.legend(loc='upper left')   #  loc 
plt.show()

numpy特有の文法で値をいじる¶

numpy

In [51]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

sample_num = 1024
x = np.arange(sample_num) / (sample_num - 1) # [0:1]
y = x ** 2 
y_modify = y.copy()           # y  copy 

index_set_1 = (y < 0.2)       # y  0.1  index 
index_set_2 = (y >= 0.2)      # y  0.1  index 
print(index_set_1)            #  True, False 
print(index_set_2)
y_modify[index_set_1] = 0.1   # index_set_1 
y_modify[index_set_2] = (y_modify[index_set_2] - 0.1) * 0.9 + 0.1

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(7,7)) # 
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,1,1)    #  index 
ax1.tick_params(axis='both', which='major', labelsize=15) # 
ax1.plot(x, y,        linestyle='--', linewidth=3, label='x^2')
ax1.plot(x, y_modify, linestyle='-',  linewidth=3, label='x^2_modify')
plt.legend(loc='upper left', fontsize=15)  #  loc 
plt.grid()
plt.show()

[ True  True  True ..., False False False]
[False False False ...,  True  True  True]

さっきの曲線をLUTとして画像に当ててみる¶

In [60]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.image as mpimg
%matplotlib inline

sample_num = 256
x = np.arange(sample_num) / (sample_num - 1) # [0:1]
y = x ** 2 
y_modify = y.copy()           # y  copy 

index_set_1 = (y < 0.2)       # y  0.1  index 
index_set_2 = (y >= 0.2)      # y  0.1  index 
y_modify[index_set_1] = 0.1   # index_set_1 
y_modify[index_set_2] = (y_modify[index_set_2] - 0.1) * 0.9 + 0.1

img = mpimg.imread('sample.jpg')

picture_shape = img.shape
# LUT1 flatten() 
r, g, b = [x.flatten() for x in np.dsplit(img, 3)]

# LUT
r_out = y_modify[r]
g_out = y_modify[g]
b_out = y_modify[b]

# RGBshape
out_img = np.dstack( (r_out, g_out, b_out) ).reshape(picture_shape)

# 
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,1) #  index 
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,2)
ax1.imshow(img)
ax2.imshow(out_img)
